data.description: Stunning country oasis! If you have been wanting a newer home with acreage, do not miss this 2021 beautiful custom built home situated on 5 pristine acres. You will appreciate the attention to detail and thought put into the design of this home. Some of this open floor plan homes features include, impressive coffered ceilings, hardwood floors throughout the main areas, an oversized laundry room, and a mudroom. The kitchen was made for entertaining, featuring an oversized bar, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry, and lots of custom all wood cabinetry with soft close doors. The large master suite offers, beautiful tray ceilings, a walk-in closet, his and hers vanities, and an oversized walk-in shower. The 3 additional bedrooms are all great sizes and also have walk-in closets. This energy efficient home includes these additional custom features: Dual hung windows, foam insulation, and an upgraded mechanical system - with a merv 11 filter, uv light kit, and mechanical fresh air ventilation. There is a full surround sound system with cat 6 wiring in a structured media enclosure. Bring all of your recreational toys, because this property already has a 36x36x18 pole barn to store your RV, boat, tractor etc.. and a 5-zone irrigation system to help maintain the curb appeal of the home. The structure was built with safety in mind, all of the walls are solid concrete, and the trusses were designed to withstand 160 mph winds. This home is perfectly located, allowing you to enjoy the peace and quiet but is still conveniently located minutes from downtown Wauchula, with supermarkets, quaint shops, great schools and a charming atmosphere. Centrally located within hours of larger cities including Tampa, Ft Myers/Naples, West Palm Beach, Orlando, etc.
